    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if the canvas is just... dead? i don't see potential. i just feel like an empty container that's taking up space. it's like having a house with no furniture, no people, no heat. just empty rooms. it feels so pointless to keep maintaining the structure when there's absolutely nothing inside worth preserving. why keep the walls up if there's nothing living in them?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
